# tree-lines
VERSION 1.0.0 // 02/27/17
Added tree guide lines to guide your eyes as you open any directory.

PLEASE NOTE:
THIS PACKAGE AS OF VERSION 0.0.1 INCLUDES A RED HIGHLIGHT MARKER TO THE VERY LEFT OF THE HIGHLIGHTED DIRECTORY/FILE.
IF YOU WOULD LIKE TO DISABLE THIS FEATURE, YOU MAY COMMENT OUT/REMOVE THE FOLLOWING LINES:

      li.directory.entry.list-nested-item.collapsed.selected::before{
        border-left: 1px solid red;
      }
      li.directory.entry.list-nested-item.expanded.selected::before{
        border-left: 1px solid red;
      }

This package is available for anyone to edit, copy or distribute.

Giving credit is not compulsory, but I would greatly appreciate it; since that small detail would support my future work.

Please, enjoy!
/Paul
